641
00:26:19,260 --> 00:26:19,690
Lin Yang?

642
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:21,290
Zhouzhou, what happened to you and Lin Yang?

643
00:26:22,690 --> 00:26:25,210
Because someone got in the way

644
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:27,810
Some boring people wrote a report letter

645
00:26:27,810 --> 00:26:29,020
