668
00:27:10,450 --> 00:27:11,380
Zhouzhou, you tell me

669
00:27:11,620 --> 00:27:12,920
What's at the end of the rainbow?

670
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:14,740
The end of the rainbow?

671
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:20,690
The rainbow is formed by the refraction of light

672
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:23,380
