679
00:27:35,210 --> 00:27:35,900
We believe you!

680
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:38,570
Zhouzhou and I do believe in you

681
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:40,050
I don't feel like eating. I'm leaving

682
